    <constraint source="spec">R6 FR-30 dedup invariant: chat + workspace SUM-CHAT siblings dedup to one render. Preserve.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Test update obligation (CLAUDE.md §10) — modify tests in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Chat/` to use stable code in test fixtures.</constraint>
  </constraints>

